    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NEW ADVENTURES! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >September 1st. Naughty Timokha burst into the assembly and ruined the holiday of knowledge! All the children ran away and only a team of brave avengers is ready to challenge real evil! Druzhban, Ded and Maloy united to fight back the enemies! In this game, you will have to survive 5 exciting days and nights, playing for different heroes and completing various quest tasks during the allotted time! Collect objects, solve the mysteries of the &quot;Tasty Pie&quot; school, survive! Only the chosen ones will be able to survive this terrible nightmare! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THIS TIME EVERYTHING IS VERY SERIOUS!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The team of villains was joined by an impudent mathematician - Tamara Pirozhkova, who will teach you how to divide a sine by a cosine! You will also be confronted by Petrovich! His weapon will be a tough ZIL, which will fire beef at our friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have an unforgettable game that will give you a lot of joy, laughter and fear at the same time!</p>",
